metadata.description:
drove the electric tricycle inside, unloaded the goods, and came to the rest place.



Sitting on the sofa in front of the window, he took out a jade pendant from his pocket and rubbed it gently.



This is a piece of dragon and phoenix jade, the quality of the jade is very bad, full of all kinds of impurities, and there are several holes in the edge, the kind of abandoned in the street no one wants.
